===Etymology=== 
From Latin '''[[trivialis]]''', ''[[crossroads]]'', where three (tri) roads (via) meet, and women stop to gossip; from '''[[tri-]]''', ''three'', + '''[[via]]''', ''way'' or ''road'', + adjective suffix '''[[-alis]]'''.

